result.title: The second training contest Per-AcT-iS#2
result.content:
Salam,

In contest rooze shanbe sa'at 14:00 shoroo mishe, hamoontor ke midoonid in contest baraye tamrin amade shode pas momken ast soalaye tekrari dar oon vojood dashte bashe, moddat in azmoun 7rooz ast, ba tashakor az MikeMirzayanov bekhatere site codeforces :)) ghabel tavajjoh ast ke in round RATED ast... soalat in contest be tartibe sakhti sort nashode va contest shamele 7 soal ast va pishnahad mishavad baraye talanbar nashodan soalat baraye rooze akhar roozi 1 dane az soalat contest ra accept konid ...

ba AREZOUYE full kardan shoma..
